text: Kissimmee surgery center Calling about your upcoming appointment Please go to our website at www. kissimmee surgery center .com Click on the pre- register link to complete or update your online medical history Again Please go to www. kissimmee surgery center .com as soon as possible If you've already completed your medical passport for Please disregard this message If we do not receive your information, we'll contact you Thank you and have a good day…”
